You both run through the crowded market jostling people aside. A cage of chickens is upset and chickens go flying in all directions.

The tiny thief is fast and it's a lot easier for her to pass through the crowd, she pulls ahead.

Thief! Stop her!

Tinker, from your vantage point on the stairs you notice all of this.

I'm going to catch her with my telescopic hand! Ooo! Natural twenty!

A mechanical hand affixed to a telescopic rod shoots through the crowd and grabs the thief by the arm.
